-its-edge-over-the-competition\">bearish outlook in May</a>, seeing that the company was likely losing its edge on Enphase (</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495151189/image_495151189.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741589-solaredge-solar-demand-may-not-recover-this-decade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 00:41:41"}, {"id": "4741587", "title": "Olema: Cash Infusion And Supply Agreement With Novartis Carries The Tide Forward", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"person working in lab\" data-id=\"2158248043\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1026px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158248043/image_2158248043.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">zhudifeng/iStock via