", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"New York: Pier 17 on South Street Seaport, Lower Manhattan.\" data-id=\"494312059\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">icon72/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Seaport Entertainment (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SEG\" title=\"Seaport Entertainment Group Inc.\">SEG</a></span>) has rallied nearly 30% since the November US election, a move that has placed the owner of entertainment-related real estate assets and operations at a marked premium from the level it was when it was split off from</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/494312059/image_494312059.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741581-seaport-entertainment-great-assets-and-growth-ahead-but-be-cautious-of-election-rally", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:45:35"}, {"id": "4741588", "title": "'Drill, Baby, Drill!'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/465352723/photo/driller-in-a-quarry.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=LuE5_rPPtskMMxL1aOKgmIJVmr9KwsYRSSC6RfkSA0g=\" alt=\"driller in a quarry\" data-id=\"465352723\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hsvrs/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong><em>Editor's Note:</em></strong> <em>Originally published at <a href=\"https://tsi-blog.com/2024/12/drill-baby-drill/\" rel=\"nofollow\">tsi-blog.com</a> on N</em><em>ovember 20, 2024</em></p> <p><em>[This blog post is an excerpt from a commentary published last week at <a href=\"https://speculative-investor.com/\" rel=\"noopener\">www.speculative-investor.com</a>]</em></p> <p>The phrase \u201cDrill baby drill\u201d has been around for a long time, but Trump</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741588-drill-baby-drill", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:41:00"}, {"id": "4741586", "title": "BlackRock's Growth Could Be Reaching A Ceiling", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Brooklyn Bridge Aerial\" data-id=\"2178095442\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2178095442/image_2178095442.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1